threads.title: 820-00165 .021ma no P5VS4RS3_EN
threads.message:
No signal of spillage on the board.

Im missing PP5V_S4RS3 and enable signal. I got a 200mv pulse on R7551 when switched on.

PM_RSMRST_L  pulses 1.35v
 PM_SLP_S4_L  pulse 400mv
